Jany Holt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jany_Holt 0 Jany Holt (13 May 1909 – 26 October 2005) was a Romanian-born actress, who worked principally in the French cinema. She was born Ruxandra Ecaterina Vladescu Olt in Bucharest, and died of natural causes in Neuilly-sur-Seine, France.Holt had appeared in 48 films and television productions between 1931 and 1995.
